This cloud function demonstrates the usage of the following aggregation operations:

group: Group statistics by dimensions like author, price range etc.
sum/avg/max/min: Common aggregation functions
push: Save detailed data in grouped results
sort: Result sorting
match: Filter aggregation results
switch: Conditional branching
subtract/multiply: Numerical calculations
year/month: Date processing
limit: Limit result count


These aggregation operations can help you perform complex data analysis and obtain valuable statistical information. You can combine these operations according to your actual needs.

