If not installed, go to:

Template Center > Template Market > Mini Program WeChat Pay for installation.

After installation, navigate to:

Template Center > My Templates > Mini Program WeChat Pay > Parameter Settings to complete necessary configurations.

Here is the calling example:

1. Create order:

```js
wx.cloud.callFunction({
  name: 'wxpay-product',
