3. Request a refund:

```js
wx.cloud.callFunction({
  name: 'wxpay-product',
  data: {
    type: 'wxpay_refund',
    orderId: 'order123', // order ID
  },
  success: (res) => {
    console.log('退款申请成功', res.result);
    // res.result :
