Notes:

1、Query product info from database, do not pass from frontend
2、Get user openid from cloud function context, do not pass from frontend
3、Store order-related info in database
4、Refund operation should update order status
5、Add proper error handling for all operations

Quickly create a cloud function in cloud run service. Upon completion, it will include callable functions like echo and log.: 

* Main path: Outputs "Hello world!"
* echo: Outputs the specific request content


You can call the function in the mini program as follows:

```js
// cloud run call required environment ID, cannot be empty
const c1 = new wx.cloud.Cloud({
  resourceEnv: 'env id'
})
await c1.init()

const r1 = await c1.callContainer({
  path: '/',   // Default function's request path
  header: {
    'X-WX-SERVICE': 'helloworld', // Fill in the name created helloworld
  },
  // Other parameters are the same as wx.request
  method: 'GET',
})
console.log(r1) //output Hello world!

const r2 = await c1.callContainer({
  path: '/echo',   // echo function's request path
  header: {
    'X-WX-SERVICE': 'helloworld', // Fill in the name created helloworld
  },
  // Other parameters are the same as wx.request
  method: 'POST',
  data: {
    a: 1,
    b: 2
  }
})
console.log(r2)  //Output the specific request and time
```

For more available content or usage methods, see [template project](https://github.com/TencentCloudBase/func-v2-template/tree/main)
